Puberty Syndrome in fourth grade,

1626
01:12:21,930 --> 01:12:27,060
you never would have met
Shouko-san at Shichirigahama Beach.

1627
01:12:28,250 --> 01:12:30,440
And if you'd never met her,

1628
01:12:30,440 --> 01:12:36,030
